### Student Course Detail Page APIs
### Lessons, exams, submissions, attendance, grades, teachers

@baseUrl = https://todu.mn/bs/lms/v1
@email = schoolstudent@must.edu.mn
@password = 123
@accessToken = p7vXn3LH7JGiL543jqmNTA

@userId = 539
@courseId = 204
@lessonId = 228
@examId = 301
@submissionId = 1
@attempt = 1


### 1. Login
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/token/email
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}",
  "push_token": ""
}


### 2. Course detail (header, description, dates)
GET {{baseUrl}}/courses/{{courseId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### 3. Course teachers (instructors section)
GET {{baseUrl}}/courses/{{courseId}}/teachers
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### 4. Course lessons list (syllabus)
GET {{baseUrl}}/courses/{{courseId}}/lessons
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### 5. Lesson detail (content + attached items)
GET {{baseUrl}}/lessons/{{lessonId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### =============== SUBMISSIONS (assignments) ===============

### 6. Submissions on a lesson (peer/teacher view — student sees own)
GET {{baseUrl}}/lessons/{{lessonId}}/submissions
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### 7. Submit assignment
POST {{baseUrl}}/lessons/{{lessonId}}/submissions
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "My submission content here",
  "user_id": {{userId}}
}


### 8. Get a submission detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/submissions/{{submissionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### 9. Edit a submission
PUT {{baseUrl}}/submissions/{{submissionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Updated submission content",
  "lesson_id": {{lessonId}},
  "user_id": {{userId}}
}


### =============== ATTENDANCE ===============

### 10. My attendance for the course
GET {{baseUrl}}/courses/{{courseId}}/attendances
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### 11. Attendance for a specific lesson
GET {{baseUrl}}/lessons/{{lessonId}}/attendances
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### 12. Course attendance point configuration
GET {{baseUrl}}/courses/{{courseId}}/attendance-points
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### =============== GRADEBOOK ===============

### 13. Overall gradebook
GET {{baseUrl}}/courses/{{courseId}}/gradebook
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### 14. Gradebook - attendances
GET {{baseUrl}}/courses/{{courseId}}/gradebook/attendances
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### 15. Gradebook - exams
GET {{baseUrl}}/courses/{{courseId}}/gradebook/exams
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### 16. Gradebook - submissions
GET {{baseUrl}}/courses/{{courseId}}/gradebook/submissions
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### =============== EXAMS (student-taking flow) ===============

### 17. Course exams list
GET {{baseUrl}}/courses/{{courseId}}/exams
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### 18. Exam detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/me/exams/{{examId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### 19. Start / resume exam attempt (creates a sheet)
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/me/exams/{{examId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}


### 20. Get my exam questions for current sheet
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/me/exams/{{examId}}/questions
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### 21. Save an answer
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/me/exams/{{examId}}/questions
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "answer": "A"
}


### 22. Finish exam
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/me/exams/{{examId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "body_text": "finish"
}


### 23. My attempts history for an exam
GET {{baseUrl}}/exams/{{examId}}/users/{{userId}}/attempts
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### 24. Attempt result / evaluation
GET {{baseUrl}}/exams/{{examId}}/users/{{userId}}/attempts/{{attempt}}/evaluation
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


### 25. Attempt questions (review after finish)
GET {{baseUrl}}/exams/{{examId}}/users/{{userId}}/attempts/{{attempt}}/questions
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
